name: Smithereens
description:
Giclée print

Size: 14x17 inches (includes 1/4" border around image)


Printed with high-quality archival inks on acid-free, fine artisan paper. This 310g, Bright White, water-resistant Fine Art Paper is made from 100% cotton fiber and is acid and lignin free and optimized for pigmented inks such as the Epson K3 Ultrachrome inks.

This print does not arrive matted or framed.

Please note that the color of the actual piece may vary from what you see on your monitor. Each print is signed, dated, and packaged with care, shipped in a padded mailer to ensure that it makes it to you unscathed. 



Artist retains all copyrights.
